{"tid":1846691,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"波都無得踢 Fake news 變真","createTime":"2020-01-27T16:59:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T17:24:31.000Z","uid":61161,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1629d919a25806d8a7cc8b6df5e6c504d61d24e4","tid":1846691,"uid":61161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T16:59:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202001/28/P2020012800027.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202001%2F28%2FP2020012800027.htm&d=gjA94EiKSJsk9JMrtOnM5hPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=b8042d7e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202001/28/P2020012800027.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n康文署設施明日起暫停開放<br />\n<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n<br />\n　　康樂及文化事務署今日（一月二十八日）宣布，為配合政府「對公共衞生有重要性的新型傳染病預備及應變計劃」下提升應變級別至緊急及避免市民聚集，以下文康設施將由明日（一月二十九日）起暫停開放，並取消在有關場地舉行的康樂、體育及文化活動，直至另行通告。<br />\n<br />\n　　暫停開放的陸上和水上運動設施包括所有體育館、運動場、草地球場、人造草地足球場、網球場、壁球場、草地滾球場、高爾夫球設施、公眾游泳池、泳灘、屯門康樂體育中心、水上活動中心和度假營。文化設施則包括所有博物館、表演場地、公共圖書館及附設之自修室、流動圖書館，以及音樂事務處的音樂中心。<br />\n<br />\n　　有關退票／款安排署方將稍後公布。<br />\n　　<br />\n完<br />\n<br />\n2020年1月28日（星期二）<br />\n香港時間0時46分"},{"pid":"3464990d923f24ed815090020c67d99b5e374015","tid":1846691,"uid":117235,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T17:00:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0OX34y3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0OX34y3.jpg&h=d930b64f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2WNPfFJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2WNPfFJ.jpg&h=033f6cbd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2f1ebeeebf7cac35054f2e7cad4e072f4cc04554","tid":1846691,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T17:15:40.000Z","msg":"gym都無得你做"},{"pid":"25dbc7a7d8c79c034eff2225f0ce7a607dd7694a","tid":1846691,"uid":257369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T17:22:45.000Z","msg":"岩岩<img sr